  paragraphs: [
    'Clay soils, high water tables and mature trees are common across the county. We inspect cracking patterns, drainage routes and ground levels to judge structural movement or flood resilience.',
    'Many villages feature retrofit insulation, replacement windows and mechanical ventilation upgrades. We assess workmanship to prevent trapped moisture, thermal bridging and condensation issues.',
    'Large estates, shared driveways and outbuildings often accompany Cheshire properties. We document boundaries, access rights and service routes so your legal team can address them early.',
  ],
